---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import SonmaiCanvas from '../components/SonmaiCanvas.astro';

const timeline = [
  {
    range: '2021–Now',
    role: 'Strategy & Product',
    org: 'Oliver Wyman',
    note: 'Advise enterprise clients on strategy, operations, and product delivery, and built The Hub, a 0-to-1 AI platform that shipped to five of them. Most recently led a ~$6M retail engagement as PM.',
  },
  {
    range: '2025–2026',
    role: 'Co-Founder',
    org: 'Lot Armor',
    note: 'Co-founded and ran a parking lot striping business. Grew it through direct sales and local partnerships, then sold it.',
  },
  {
    range: '2020–2021',
    role: 'Program Manager',
    org: 'Microsoft',
    note: 'Led a 10-person team through a Fortune 50 IT divestiture, managing $6M in engagement funds and a ~20K-item backlog.',
  },
  {
    range: '2018',
    role: 'Software Engineering Intern',
    org: 'NAL Technologies',
    note: 'Built GPS, audio, and tracking features in Java and C for one of the first fully integrated satellite smartphones, developed for DoD applications.',
  },
  {
    range: '2016–2020',
    role: 'B.A. Computer Science & Entrepreneurship',
    org: 'University of Virginia',
    note: 'Graduated With Distinction and Phi Beta Kappa with a 3.9 GPA. Founding member of 180 Degrees Consulting and a discrete mathematics teaching assistant.',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About · Justin Nguyễn"
  description="Where Justin Nguyễn comes from, and what he is building toward."
>
  <div class="page">
    <SonmaiCanvas />

    <Nav active="about" variant="overlay" />

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-scrim"></div>
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="eyebrow hero-eyebrow">About</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Where I come from, and what I'm building toward.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-cue">&darr;</div>
    </section>

    <div class="body">
      <div class="bio">
        <p class="lead-para">
          I'm a strategist and a builder. For the past six years I've moved between consulting and
          product work, starting where the strategy gets set and staying through the part where it
          actually gets built. That's the work I care about: not the deck, but what happens after the
          deck.
        </p>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            My family is from Việt Nam. I grew up between two cultures, and I'm set on not letting
            that heritage thin out in me. I'm relearning the language so I can talk with my
            grandparents in it, and one day write my own poetry in it. I keep Vietnamese music in
            rotation constantly, and the craft traditions I grew up around, especially sơn mài
            lacquerware, shaped how I think about building things: layer by layer, with patience,
            until the depth starts to show.
          </p>
          <p>
            That same instinct is what I do for a living. It started with slide decks and financial
            models, the language of consulting, and grew into shipping software and standing up
            products from nothing. Hand me something tangled and half-defined, and I'll try to give it
            a shape and ship something. That's what I keep doing whether anyone asks me to or not.
          </p>
          <p>
            Much of that happens in the room, not on the page. I've spent years in steering committees
            and executive meetings, making the case for an idea or turning something complicated into
            a story a leader can act on in the next 30 minutes. I'm at home reading a room and working
            with the personalities in it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>The path</h2>
        <div class="rule path-rule"></div>
        {
          timeline.map((t) => (
            <div class="entry">
              <div class="range">{t.range}</div>
              <div>
                <div class="role">{t.role}</div>
                <div class="org">{t.org}</div>
                <p class="note">{t.note}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <div class="section beyond">
        <h2>Beyond the work</h2>
        <div class="rule beyond-rule"></div>
        <p class="beyond-copy">
          Outside of work, I'm almost always training. I swam competitively as a kid, moved into
          bodybuilding after college, and eventually landed on hybrid training for the way it forces
          strength and endurance to coexist. I've raced HYROX, and an Ironman is on the horizon. I
          think about longevity a lot, and I treat my health like a long-term project, not a phase.
          The other constant is food: I'll track down a good restaurant anywhere I go, and the first
          thing I look for in a new city is its best Vietnamese spot.
        </p>
        <p class="beyond-copy">
          I grew up on superheroes and never lost the habit of wanting to build something bigger than
          what's in front of me. That instinct is what led me to tech, to AI, and to the kinds of
          companies I want to be part of next.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section cta-wrap">
        <div class="cta">
          <div class="status">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="status-text">
              Currently exploring operator and product roles at growth-stage companies.
            </span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="cta-title">Let's talk.</h2>
          <p class="cta-copy">
            If you're building something ambiguous and real, I'd love to hear about it.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-links">
            <a href="mailto:justintknguyen@gmail.com">Email</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/justintknguyen/">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/daherro">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <Footer />
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { position: relative; }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 620px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }
  .hero-scrim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10, 7, 6, 0.5) 0%, rgba(10, 7, 6, 0) 22%, rgba(10, 7, 6, 0) 52%, rgba(10, 7, 6, 0.72) 100%);
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: var(--maxw); width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--pad-x) 92px var(--pad-x); }
  .hero-eyebrow { margin-bottom: 24px; text-shadow: 0 1px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    margin: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0.04em;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5.6vw, 80px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-brightest);
    max-width: 880px;
    text-shadow: 0 3px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
  }
  .scroll-cue {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: 28px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 3;
    color: #d8cfbc;
    font-size: 22px;
    animation: bob 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes bob {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, 7px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .body { position: relative; z-index: 2; background: var(--bg); border-top: 1px solid rgba(227, 184, 100, 0.22); }
  .bio { max-width: var(--maxw-read); margin: 0 auto; padding: 96px 32px 52px 32px; }
  .lead-para {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.4vw, 38px);
    line-height: 1.32;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .prose { font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ink-softer); margin-top: 40px; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 26px 0; }
  .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .pull { margin: 52px 0; padding: 0 0 0 30px; border-left: 2px solid var(--celadon-deep); }
  .pull p { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-size: clamp(26px, 3.4vw, 34px); line-height: 1.36; color: var(--celadon); margin: 0; }

  .section { max-width: var(--maxw-read); margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 32px 0 32px; }
  .section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 30px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-bright); margin: 0 0 8px 0; }
  .path-rule { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .entry { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 28px; padding: 30px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(227, 184, 100, 0.14); }
  .range { font-size: 14px; color: var(--celadon); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; padding-top: 0.5em; }
  .role { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.15; }
  .org { font-size: 15px; color: var(--celadon); margin-top: 4px; }
  .note { margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--muted); }

  .beyond { padding-top: 64px; }
  .beyond-rule { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .beyond-copy { margin: 0; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ink-softer); }
  .beyond-copy + .beyond-copy { margin-top: 26px; }

  .cta-wrap { padding: 64px 32px 96px 32px; }
  .cta { border: 1px solid var(--rule); border-radius: 3px; padding: 44px 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(227, 184, 100, 0.05), rgba(227, 184, 100, 0)); }
  .status { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 11px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .dot { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--celadon-dot); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(143, 176, 155, 0.18), 0 0 14px rgba(143, 176, 155, 0.7); }
  .status-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--celadon); }
  .cta-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px); font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-bright); margin: 0; line-height: 1.12; }
  .cta-copy { margin: 14px 0 28px 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--muted-link); max-width: 520px; }
  .cta-links { display: flex; gap: 26px; font-size: 15px; }
  .cta-links a { color: var(--gold); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(227, 184, 100, 0.45); padding-bottom: 2px; transition: color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease; }
  .cta-links a:hover { color: var(--ink-bright); border-color: var(--ink-bright); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .entry { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 8px; }
    .range { padding-top: 0; }
  }
</style>
